## 5. Typography rules

| Class | Font | Weight | Size | Use |
|-------|------|--------|------|-----|
| `.cins-display` | Anton | 400 | 88px | Decorative poster headlines only |
| `.cins-h1` | Be Vietnam Pro | 800 | 48px | Page titles (màu `--cins-blue`) |
| `.cins-h2` | Be Vietnam Pro | 700 | 36px | Section headings |
| `.cins-h3` | Be Vietnam Pro | 600 | 22px | Card titles, sub-sections |
| `.cins-h4` | Be Vietnam Pro | 600 | 18px | Small headings |
| `.cins-eyebrow` | Be Vietnam Pro | 500 | 14px | Labels above headings |
| `.cins-body` | Be Vietnam Pro | 400 | 16px | Body text |
| `.cins-body-lg` | Be Vietnam Pro | 400 | 18px | Lead paragraphs |
| `.cins-caption` | Be Vietnam Pro | 400 | 14px | Meta, captions |
| `.cins-editorial` | Crimson Pro | 400 | 18px | Long-form article body |
| `.cins-pullquote` | Crimson Pro | 600i | 28px | Pull quotes |

**Rules:**
- Be Vietnam Pro cho tất cả UI. Anton chỉ cho decorative display (sparingly).
- Crimson Pro chỉ cho long-form article body và pull quotes.
- H1/H2/H3 màu `--cins-blue` theo brand spec.
- Body text luôn dùng `--ink-body` (rgba softened, KHÔNG pure black).
- **Sentence case everywhere.** KHÔNG all-caps, KHÔNG Title Case For Every Word.
- Vietnamese-first: giữ diacritics đúng. Loanwords giữ tiếng Anh (Animator, Game Designer, VFX...).

